    <article id="section-interaction">
      <h2 class="site-article-headline hca-typography--headline">Interaction</h2>
      <br />
      <section class="site-section">
        <h3 class="hca-typography--title">Row Hover (large screen)</h3>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Display a background in a table row if a user hovers over any part of that row. If there are separate hover states on individual table cells, display both the hover state of the cell and row at the same time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-8">
            <figure class="hca-visual-example">
              <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/data-tables/row-hover.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="" />
              <figcaption class="hca-visual-example__caption hca-typography--caption">Hovering over a row</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{!-- / row --}}
      </section>
      <section class="site-section">
        <h3 class="hca-typography--title">Row Selection</h3>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">When a row is selected, display a background color on the row.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-8">
            <figure class="hca-visual-example">
              <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/data-tables/row-selection.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="" />
              <figcaption class="hca-visual-example__caption hca-typography--caption">Selected table rows</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{!-- / row --}}
      </section>
      <section class="site-section">
        <h3 class="hca-typography--title">Column Sorting</h3>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">If column sorting is enabled, sort the most important data by default and display a sorted state in the column header. If the user clicks on a column that is already sorted, reverse the sort order and rotate the sort icon.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-8">
            <figure class="hca-visual-example">
              <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/data-tables/sorted-column.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="" />
              <figcaption class="hca-visual-example__caption hca-typography--caption">Table with a column sorted in descending order</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{!-- / row --}}
      </section>

      <section class="site-section">
        <h3 class="hca-typography--title">Column Name Hover (Large Screen)</h3>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="site-container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">If there is a need to provide definitions to column headers, display a tooltip on hover. If sorting is enabled, display a light sort icon upon hover, which indicates that the column is sortable.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-8">
            <figure class="hca-visual-example">
              <img src="{{page.base_url}}images/components/data-tables/column-hover.png" class="img-responsive hca-visual-example__comp" alt="" />
              <figcaption class="hca-visual-example__caption hca-typography--caption">Hovering over a column name</figcaption>
            </figure>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{!-- / row --}}
      </section>
    </article>
